title: What to Do When You Doubt You Have What It Takes
description: Do you have a big dream but seriously doubt you're cut out for it? You're not alone. But instead of encouraging you with a bunch of cliche motivational quotes, J is handing you a roadmap with specific, practical steps you can take when you feel the fear but need to find a way to do it anyway.
author: matt@jordanleedooley.com (Jordan Lee Dooley)
